WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.080 --> 00:00:12.900
Architects of the Cathedrals built 800
years ago,

00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:16.160
the engineers of the International Space Station,

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:18.620
Picasso the painter,

00:00:18.620 --> 00:00:24.160
the inventors of Google Glass - what do
these people have in common?

00:00:24.180 --> 00:00:28.680
You! You can learn from these pioneers how to
be successful,

00:00:28.689 --> 00:00:33.329
how to achieve your own innovations, how
to make your own discoveries.

00:00:33.329 --> 00:00:38.009
You can learn the skills that make you a
pioneer as well.

00:00:38.060 --> 00:00:42.980
“How?”, you ask. We have created a learning experience for you where remarkable 

00:00:42.980 --> 00:00:49.110
professors and experts from around the world share their insights on how to overcome challenges,

00:00:49.110 --> 00:00:53.810
how to solve complex problems and how to
reach goals.

00:00:55.530 --> 00:00:57.390
We are Leuphana Digital School,

00:00:57.390 --> 00:00:59.030
and Zeppelin University,

00:00:59.030 --> 00:01:02.260
and Harvard University, and University
of Luxembourg

00:01:02.260 --> 00:01:06.300
and Central University of Finance and Economics China...

00:01:08.060 --> 00:01:14.520
Their professors and experts have teamed up to create a course for you that is delivered exclusively online.

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:19.680
Everybody who wishes to participate in this unique opportunity is invited to do so -

00:01:19.770 --> 00:01:23.450
it is free of charge and there are no
prerequisites.

00:01:23.450 --> 00:01:30.330
Well, actually that is not true. You need
to have the desire that all innovators share: 

00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:32.760
the desire to create something new.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:38.260
Most it was find that being innovative is a hard and lonely job.

00:01:38.400 --> 00:01:43.300
While we pursue our innovative ideas, we encounter resistance to change,

00:01:43.300 --> 00:01:47.740
big knowledge gaps and many problems monsters. 

00:01:47.740 --> 00:01:51.980
Through your participation in our course you will learn to chase them away 

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:56.840
and even to turn them into your friends to reach your goals together.

00:01:57.710 --> 00:02:01.289
You will form teams with participants
from all over the world

00:02:01.289 --> 00:02:04.350
to learn from each other how to become a
pioneer

00:02:04.350 --> 00:02:07.410
under the guidance of specially trained
mentors.

00:02:07.540 --> 00:02:13.980
Throughout the course you will be provided with input via video lectures and online teaching material.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:21.140
The course is highly interactive with assignments and discussions inside your team and with the other teams.

00:02:21.140 --> 00:02:25.879
You will form a global community of
collective learning.

00:02:25.879 --> 00:02:31.019
Over the course of "Solution and Innovation Skills" we will cover 12 topics.

00:02:31.060 --> 00:02:38.080
For each topic one of the professors or experienced experts will share with you their research based insights

00:02:38.090 --> 00:02:41.050
on how to be innovative and
successful.

00:02:41.060 --> 00:02:46.180
In the assignments that you receive you can apply these insights right away.

00:02:46.560 --> 00:02:49.620
You will cover these topics over a total of 10 weeks. 

00:02:49.940 --> 00:02:55.000
Since this course is internet based, you will study from the comfort of your own desk at home

00:02:55.010 --> 00:02:58.990
or with your mobile device from wherever you wish to be.

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:02.780
In addition, you will take various online
based assessments

00:03:02.780 --> 00:03:06.940
with unique feedback tools during the
course, which measure your ability

00:03:06.940 --> 00:03:09.580
to develop solutions and to be
innovative. 

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:15.140
They will provide you with valuable feedback and enable you to keep track of your progress.

00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:20.200
Of course your individual results are treated as strictly confidential.

00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:24.880
After successfully completing the course
by finishing all assignments,

00:03:25.000 --> 00:03:31.000
you can obtain a University Certificate with five credits for an administrative fee of only € 20.

00:03:31.560 --> 00:03:34.960
It is our target to make you a better
innovator,

00:03:34.970 --> 00:03:39.500
a sharper pioneer, and more successful in
reaching your goals.

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:45.120
That is why we are looking forward to
having you with us on our journey of discovery.

